	<div class="grid gap-8">
		<section id="section-about">
			<p class="leading-8 mb-8">
			Hi! I'm Ron and science, technology, programming, basketball, and automobiles are just a few of the things that I'm passionate about. I enjoy opportunities to try new things, share ideas, solve problems and make connections. I love it when I get the chance to explore how a new system, or device works. I started sharing what I've learned so far and what I&#39m learning now on
			my
			<a href="/blog" rel="prefetch" class="underline text-blue-500 hover:text-slate-500">blog</a>.
			</p>
		</section>
		<section id="section-portfolio">
			<h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-5xl mt-4 mb-4 font-bold text-center">My Work</h2>
			<PortfolioPreview project={featuredProject} />
			<div class="my-8 text-center">
			<a href="/projects/" class="button" rel="prefetch">View All</a>
			</div>
		</section>
		<section id="section-contact">
			<h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-5xl mb-4 font-bold text-center">Get In Touch</h2>
			<p>
			Building something special and want to chat? I would love to hear
			about it! Send me an email and we can
			schedule a time to talk.
			</p>
			<div class="flex items-center gap-4 mt-3 mx-auto max-w-fit">
			<span
				class="w-9 h-9 flex items-center justify-center border-t border-zinc-700 rounded-full"
				><img
				class="hover:animate-bounce-slow focus:animate-bounce-slow"
				src={send}
				alt="send email to jeanfrancoisron@gmail.com"
				height={20}
				width={20}
				/>
			</span>
			<a
				href="mailto:jeanfrancoisron@gmail.com"
				class="text-lg text-blue-500 underline hover:text-slate-500 focus:text-slate-500"
				>jeanfrancoisron@gmail.com</a
			>
			</div>
		</section>
	</div>
</MainLayout>
